name: Black and White Roses Crop Top
description:
The crop top has made a return. Perfect for days at the beach, festivals and of course... high wasited shorts!

This crop top is made from a thick, stiffened material with a slight stretch. Framed with a feminine frill, the top is gathered into a bow to allow for extra material across the chest, meaning it is suitable for small and large busted women. 

This top ties up at the back into a bow or double knot, allowing it to fit many shapes, sizes and tightness levels.

One size fits most.

name: Tie Up Flower Maxi Dress
description:
A summer-inspired maxi dress, featuring a comfortable elastic waist, drawing the fabric and eye to the smallest part of the body. 

This fluent, versatile maxi can be worn two ways as seen in the picture - tied up at the front to form a bow across the chest (pictured right), or for more coverage it can be tied up to form a bow at the back (pictured left).

This dress uses locally sourced flower print cotton in orange and purple and thick black cotton/polyester. Proudly designed and made in Australia. 

One size fits all.
